Module: AddActivity/MainActivity
Functions: Adding new Items into database (later firebase only)
Inputs: TaskName, startTime, startdate, endTime, endDate, recurringDays[]
Results: new ToDoItem(TaskName, startTime, startdate, endTime, endDate, recurringDays[])
         inserted into hash values of all keys matching recurringDays[]


Module: NotificationReceiver/MoodNotificationReceiver
Functions: Registering notification channel, building new notifications
Inputs: Title, time
Results: Everyday at the given time AlarmManager triggers intent that carries metadata that the receiver
         needs to build a habit/mood notification.
        
